ecting actual vulnerability patterns. Important research for understanding AI-assisted code review reliability.\",\n    \"author\": \"Multiple researchers (arXiv:2602.16741)\",\n    \"source\": \"Paper\",\n    \"url\": \"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.16741v1\",\n    \"published_date\": \"2026-02-18\",\n    \"topics\": [\"llm-code-review\", \"security\", \"vulnerability-detection\", \"arxiv\", \"research\", \"code-quality\"],\n    \"type\": \"technical\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Two Minute Papers: Google Gemini 3.1 Pro Review Video\",\n    \"description\": \"Two Minute Papers released a video review of Google Gemini 3.1 Pro that gained over 1 million views within 1 hour. Video demonstrates the model's capabilities, compares it against GPT-5.2, and covers three major scenarios where it outperformed competitors. Continues channel's mission of making AI concepts accessible without complex academic terminology.\",\n    \"author\": \"Two Minute Papers (Károly Zsolnai-Fehér)\",\n    \"source\": \"YouTube\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/@TwoMinutePapers\",\n    \"published_date\": \"2026-02-20\",\n    \"topics\": [\"two-minute-papers\", \"gemini\", \"model-review\", \"ai-education\", \"benchmarks\", \"google\"],\n    \"type\": \"technical\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"AI Engineer Handbook: Comprehensive Resource Curated for 2026\",\n    \"description\": \"GitHub repository 'AI Engineer Handbook' published February 17, 2026, compiling essential resources for AI engineers. Recommends top educational creators including 3Blue1Brown (6M+ followers), Yannic Kilcher (250K+), Two Minute Papers (1.5M+), and AI Explained (500K+). Represents curated knowledge map for AI engineering careers in 2026.\",\n    \"author\": \"DataExpert-io (GitHub)\",\n    \"source\": \"Platform\",\n    \"url\": \"https://github.com/DataExpert-io/ai-engineer-handbook\",\n    \"published_date\": \"2026-02-17\",\n    \"topics\": [\"ai-engineering\", \"education\", \"resources\", \"github\", \"le